use to enter your

the relevant information simply click on
send feedback
to comment on a specific Knowledge
Center article use the comment section
under the
article this is usually located at the
bottom of the page
here to provide feedback on AWS
documentation you have two options on
the documentation homepage choose the
feedback link located here at the top of
the
page or on any documentation page choose
provide feedback this link is located at
the bottom of the
page when you choose the feedback button
